ActCustoms Act
SubjectCustoms Controlled Areas Regulations
PrecisCUSTOMS CONTROLLED AREAS REGULATIONS in order to (1) assist in reducing the flow of drugs or contraband into Canada; (2) improve intelligence information on smuggling behaviours at Canada's Ports of entries; and (3) assist in disrupting the activities of organized crime.
